      <title>现金紧缩迹象导致香港人民币融资成本飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/yuan-funding-costs-jump-in-hong-kong-amid-signs-of-cash-squeeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港的人民币借贷成本升至近两年来的最高水平，表明人民币在香港的稀缺性——并提醒交易者注意北京曾经采用的货币升值策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/yuan-funding-costs-jump-in-hong-kong-amid-signs-of-cash-squeeze</guid>
