      <title>韩国敦促贷方增加项目融资债务准备金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/korea-urges-lenders-to-boost-provisions-for-project-finance-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国敦促金融机构增加项目融资债务损失准备金，理由是陷入困境的建筑项目有所增加，储蓄银行的拖欠率也在上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/korea-urges-lenders-to-boost-provisions-for-project-finance-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 06:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将进一步扩大油籽产量以减少进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-to-further-expand-oilseed-production-to-reduce-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[明年，中国将在更多土地上种植油菜籽，并稳定大豆种植面积，扩大政策推动力，提高油籽收成，减少最大消费国对海外供应的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-to-further-expand-oilseed-production-to-reduce-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 06:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，中国扩大了对保险公司的股票出售限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-is-said-to-expand-stock-selling-restrictions-to-insurers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，中国正在将股票净卖出禁令从主要共同基金扩大到一些保险公司，这是当局试图支撑暴跌股市的又一迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-is-said-to-expand-stock-selling-restrictions-to-insurers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 06:12:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
